Exam 3 – Library Management System
A library manages books and borrowings.
•	Each book has: title, author, copies available.
•	Rules:
o	A member can borrow max 3 books at a time.
o	If return is late → fine = 2 units per day.
o	If copies = 0 → book cannot be borrowed.
•	Tasks:
1.	Input members + borrowing requests.
2.	Track which books are borrowed/returned.
3.	Print status of all members + fines + available books.

